  "detailed_description": "<h1>QQ群</h1><p><strong>官方玩家QQ群：757629696</strong> 欢迎来一起来讨论游戏，反馈问题~</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/66fa3fcd4ca6e283890471053ba5074c.poster.avif?t=1745408557\" width=650 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/66fa3fcd4ca6e283890471053ba5074c.webm?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/66fa3fcd4ca6e283890471053ba5074c.mp4?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>可爱的角色在诡异的宅邸中探寻真相，精致的像素画面，有趣的探索，搭配精美的CG插图，和主角赛莉卡一起冒险吧。<br><br>玩家在游戏中会获得各种各样的道具<br>“火柴”“探灵仪”“创可贴”等等，除了用以解开谜题以外，有些也会在探索的过程中给玩家提供便利与帮助。<br>另外，玩家在游戏中也可能突然遭遇各种各样危险。遇到这种情况的时候请善加利用各种道具和游戏的存档机制。<br>对了，说到存档，抱歉游戏中没有即时存档。所以，在看到存档点的时候，一定要记得存档哦。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/1920924248c890fc10392947d46b35e4.poster.avif?t=1745408557\" width=650 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/1920924248c890fc10392947d46b35e4.webm?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/1920924248c890fc10392947d46b35e4.mp4?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏中含有大量像素小人的动作表演，主角在与各种物品互动的时候，会有很细致的表演和反馈哟。<br>当然，在旅途中还会碰到形形色色的事物，他们也会有很多有趣的表现，请务必大胆和他们互动一番！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/828f7b43bb36e1818ca02b1e966abccf.poster.avif?t=1745408557\" width=99 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/828f7b43bb36e1818ca02b1e966abccf.webm?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/edc0a29bdb78e383a292e324da1cd464.poster.avif?t=1745408557\" width=99 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/edc0a29bdb78e383a292e324da1cd464.webm?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/60cd8e665619987de5c8e99ca3cfb2ee.poster.avif?t=1745408557\" width=650 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/60cd8e665619987de5c8e99ca3cfb2ee.webm?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406110/extras/60cd8e665619987de5c8e99ca3cfb2ee.mp4?t=1745408557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这座房子里也并非只有赛莉卡一人，在探索的过程中，可能会邂逅其他的npc，他们性格各异，有着不同的行为逻辑和各自的秘密。<br>不过，究竟他们是敌是友，这就不得而知了。<br><br>最后，游戏中含有多个结局以及最后的真结局，不同结局的分支前会有较为明显的存档提示，请大胆抉择吧！",
